  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, until pink and cooked through.",
    "Remove the shrimp from the skillet and set aside.",
    "Add the chopped chervil, lemon juice, and orange zest to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Return the shrimp to the skillet and toss to coat with the citrus and chervil sauce.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the shrimp hot, garnished with additional chervil if desired."
